<plot>The true story of a 1920's Canadian jazz band who play their every performance gagged and almost completely immobilized by thick cords which bind them hand and foot. The music they produce - from a full range of instruments, yet without recourse to the usual limbs and orifices - is a moving triumph of courage over self imposed adversity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?264464</url></doc>
